        <abstract> 
<p>W. Crookes’s article ["Enquiry into phenomena called spiritual", <hi rend="italic">Q. J. Sci.</hi> n.s. 4 (1874): 77–97] "staggers" her. Would like to know CD’s opinion.</p> 
        </abstract>
